    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Discretization error factor exceeds requirements (achieved level 3 vs required level 2). Validation results demonstrate NRMSE of 8.3% against FDA experimental data, within the 15% acceptance threshold. Mesh convergence GCI of 1.4% confirms adequate spatial resolution. Six factors appropriately scoped out per MRL 2 profile requirements. Compound assessment concludes the CFD model has sufficient credibility to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device regulatory submission.",
